d by central nervous system (CNS) fatigue for months.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_nervous_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"central nervous system (CNS)\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_nervous_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_nervous_system\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yang\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, she could not move her body freely in the pool and, as a result, could not practice.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the worst case at that time, after swimming a few hundred meters, I would not be able to lift my arms,\\\" Yang told the China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worst case\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"a few hundred meters\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"my arms\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"Yang\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"CMG\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I continued, I would need people to rescue me from the pool.\\\"\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What makes CNS fatigue so frustrating was that, unlike normal injuries, it does not have a clear source.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"CNS fatigue\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"normal injuries\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear source\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, Yang, her coach and medical staff did not know where to begin when they tried to fix the problem.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yang, her coach and medical staff\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fortunately for Yang, she managed to recover in the end, and recovered her form before the Olympic Trials.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794952675, \"rank\": 0.03896103896103429, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yang\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"her form\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It made me think a lot about training and competing,\\\" Yang said.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"Yang\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I realized that everyone has their own pace.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"their own pace\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not need to match others' progress.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others' progress\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just need to find my own pace.\\\"\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own pace\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yang also performed well in the women's 200-meter freestyle event at the Olympic Trials.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yang\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 200-meter freestyle event\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Trials\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her time of 1:54.37 is the fourth-best in the world this year.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her time\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"1:54.37\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Olympics in 2021, she helped China win gold in the women's 200-meter freestyle relay.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999447482, \"rank\": 5.523909778699115e-11, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.743884401858233, \"r